features: EFFICIENT SKINCARE DEVICE FOR YOUR FEET: Want to have silky, smooth feet? Tired of wasting time and money on salon appointments? Treat your feet effortlessly yet effectively with a professional procedure anytime, anywhere. The Essy Premium Electric Foot File hard skin remover has 3 types of chargeable rollers to suit your needs: a fine roller for thin layer of dead skin on the feet, a regular roller for thicker layer and a coarse roller for thick layer, cracked heels or troublesome calluses.

SAFETY TECHNOLOGY: This electronic foot file rechargeable callus remover has an implemented “Pressure lock” technology, which automatically stops the device if you apply too much force while using it. With this safety feature, you are ensured of a safe and pleasant procedure. Do not push the device into your skin. Take your time and let this foot scraper hard skin work its magic.

USER-ORIENTED FEATURES: Aside from being an ergonomic, multipurpose device, this carry-anywhere, gentle callus remover has a lot of awesome features to fit your needs: 2 adjustable grinding speeds, light to help you illuminate hard-to-reach places, convenient USB charging, and a LED display screen. What’s more, this dead skin remover for feet is water-resistant and can be rinsed under water while cleaning.

WHAT’S IN THE BOX: Our electrical dead skin exfoliator extraordinaire comes with all the accessories you need to achieve silky, smooth and great-looking feet: device, head cover, 3 types of grinding heads (fine, medium and coarse rollers), USB charging cable, a brush for cleaning purposes, and a user manual. Our foot files for hard skin professional also comes with 2x additional replacement rollers, saving you the trouble of spending time and money on reordering.
